<P>We have now to reckon arrears of intere&s;t, and the gro&s;s &s;um not yet paying intere&s;t. The intere&s;t of the foreign debt being already &s;uppo&s;ed to be con&s;olidated with the principal, and to make it 10,000,000 dollars, there is nothing to be &s;et down for foreign arrears.</P>
